      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="15433517">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/myluoye/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1124367-1.jpg" alt="洛烨" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/15433517/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/15433517/" class="">第98页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/myluoye/" class=" " title="洛烨">洛烨</a>
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="15433517">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">自由是实践宇宙（凭借上帝的力量制定的）规律；一个人被诱惑而想施加给这个规律的阻力越小，他就会越快乐和自由。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2011-11-20 11:50</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>自由是实践宇宙（凭借上帝的力量制定的）规律；一个人被诱惑而想施加给这个规律的阻力越小，他就会越快乐和自由。</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







